fullplot: The life, career and music of singer Katy Perry as we follow her on the California Dreams tour.
plot: The life, career and music of singer Katy Perry as we follow her on the California Dreams tour.
title: Katy Perry: Part of Me

tomatoes.consensus: Katy Perry: Part of Me succeeds on the strengths of the pop star's genuine likability, inspiring work ethic, and dazzling stage show, even if it plays somewhat like a PR puff piece at times.
